"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\"><img alt=\"Harvey Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7a/Harvey_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\">Harvey</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\"><img alt=\"Jodi Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Jodi_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\">Jodi</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\"><img alt=\"Kent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/86/Kent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\">Kent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\"><img alt=\"Krobus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/10/Krobus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\"><img alt=\"Leah Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6e/Leah_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\">Leah</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\"><img alt=\"Lewis Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Lewis_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\"><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\"><img alt=\"Marnie Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Marnie_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bone_Mill\">Bone Mill</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mummified_Frog&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bone Mill\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Mummified Frog can be turned into <a href=\"/Quality_Fertilizer\" title=\"Quality Fertilizer\">Quality Fertilizer</a>, <a href=\"/Speed-Gro\" title=\"Speed-Gro\">Speed-Gro</a>, <a href=\"/Deluxe_Speed-Gro\" title=\"Deluxe Speed-Gro\">Deluxe Speed-Gro</a> or <a href=\"/Tree_Fertilizer\" title=\"Tree Fertilizer\">Tree Fertilizer</a> in the <a href=\"/Bone_Mill\" title=\"Bone Mill\">Bone Mill</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mummified_Frog&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mummified Frog is used in the spool of a <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Skeleton Shirt</a>. <a href=\"/File:Shirt014.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt014.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/0f/Shirt014.png/24px-Shirt014.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0f/Shirt014.png 1.5x\" /></a> It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mummified_Frog&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Quests#Fragments_of_the_past\" title=\"Quests\">\"Fragments of the past\"</a>: <a href=\"/Gunther\" title=\"Gunther\">Gunther</a> may make a request on the <a href=\"/Quests#List_of_Special_Orders\" title=\"Quests\">Special Orders board</a> for 100 of any combination of bone items that must be gathered while the quest is active. You have 7 days to complete the quest. The reward is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"3500\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />3,500g</span> and the <a href=\"/Bone_Mill\" title=\"Bone Mill\">Bone Mill</a> recipe.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mummified_Frog&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Introduced.</li></ul>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414153454\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.125 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.139 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1901/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 13212/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 787/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 517 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   61.351      1 -total\n 61.35%   37.636      1 Template:Infobox\n 38.24%   23.462      1 Template:Description\n 29.34%   18.003      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  5.45%    3.344      3 Template:Price\n  5.44%    3.336      1 Template:History\n  2.92%    1.789      1 Template:Version\n  2.43%    1.492      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  2.27%    1.394      1 Template:Clear\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:11647-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414153454 and revision id 189429\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng       = Mummified Frog\n|source    = <nowiki />\n*[[Ginger Island]] Jungle\n*[[The Mines#Shrine of Challenge|Dangerous Mines]] (Floors 41-69)\n|sellprice = 100\n|quality   = false\n}}\nThe '''Mummified Frog''' is an item that can be obtained by cutting jungle [[weeds]] in the [[Ginger Island#Island East|Ginger Island jungle]] or in floors 40 – 69 of the [[The Mines#Shrine of Challenge|Dangerous Mines]]. Jungle weeds normally have a 1% chance to drop a Mummified Frog, except for the first Mummified Frog found after unlocking the [[Island Field Office]], which has a 10% chance instead.\n\n[[File:JungleWeeds.png|thumb|left|Weeds that drop the Mummified Frog]]{{clear}}\n\n==Donations==\nThe Mummified Frog can be donated to the [[Island Field Office]], which rewards 1 [[Golden Walnut]].\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|hate=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n}}\n\n==Bone Mill==\nThe Mummified Frog can be turned into [[Quality Fertilizer]], [[Speed-Gro]], [[Deluxe Speed-Gro]] or [[Tree Fertilizer]] in the [[Bone Mill]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nMummified Frog is used in the spool of a [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Skeleton Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt014.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\n*[[Quests#Fragments of the past|\"Fragments of the past\"]]: [[Gunther]] may make a request on the [[Quests#List of Special Orders|Special Orders board]] for 100 of any combination of bone items that must be gathered while the quest is active. You have 7 days to complete the quest. The reward is {{Price|3500}} and the [[Bone Mill]] recipe.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Introduced.}}\n\n[[Category:Field Office donations]]\n\n[[de:Mumifizierter Frosch]]\n[[es:Rana momificada]]\n[[fr:Grenouille momifiée]]\n[[it:Rana mummificata]]\n[[ja:カエルのミイラ]]\n[[ko:미이라화된 개구리]]\n[[hu:Mumifikált béka]]\n[[pt:Sapo Mumificado]]\n[[ru:Мумифицированная лягушка]]\n[[tr:Mumyalanmış Kurbağa]]\n[[zh:青蛙木乃伊]]"
    }
